'''Fix Us''' ni firime yo muri [[Gana]] ya 2019 yakozwe na Yvonne Nelson kandi iyobowe na Pascal Amanfo.  Filime yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Gana Movie Awards<ref>https://www.broadcastprome.com/news/netflix-streams-ghanian-film-fix-us/</ref> .

== Umugambi ==
Abakobwa batatu bakiri bato bafite icyifuzo cyo kuba superstars bahurira ahakorerwa igenzura aho bari bafite inzozi zisa<ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2019/12/coming-soon-fix-us.html</ref>, babaye inshuti hanyuma nyuma  ubuzima bwabo bwarose ariko bumva ko hari ikintu kibuze mubuzima bwabo nyuma yo kugera ku bwamamare n'ubutunzi<ref>https://www.graphic.com.gh/entertainment/showbiz-news/yvonne-nelson-s-movie-fix-us-to-stream-on-netflix.html</ref>.  

