== Umusaruro ==
Abakinnyi benshi b'Abanyafurika bamenyekanye ko bakinnye muri iyi filime, barimo Yvonne Okoro, igikomangoma David Osei, na Michelle Attoh<ref>https://www.filmoneng.com/fix-us/</ref>. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu gukina imbuga nkoranyambaga Hajia4real n'umucuranzi Irene Logan<ref>https://www.ghbase.com/yvonne-nelsons-fix-us-movie-to-premiere-on-netflix/</ref>.  

== Kurekura ==
''Fix Us'' yerekanwe bwa mbere muri [[Gana]] ku ya 6 Ukuboza 2019 mu nzu mberabyombi ya Silverbird i [[Accra]], nyuma yerekanwa muri [[Gana]] ndetse no mu tundi turere twa [[Afurika]].   Muri 2020 firime yerekanwe kuri Netflix<ref>https://www.elle.ci/people-lifestyle/culture/netflix-fix-us-le-film-de-yvonne-nelson-avec-yvonne-okoro-et-alexandra-amon-enfin-disponible/</ref>. 

== Kwakira ==
Pulse Nigeria yashyize ahagaragara ''Fix Us'' nk'imwe muri filime nshya nziza zo muri [[Gana]] z'umwaka, aho ikinyamakuru  ''Glitz Africa'' kivuga ko yakiriwe neza nyuma yo gusohoka<ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/entertainment/Yvonne-Nelson-hits-big-with-Fix-Us-Friday-opening-808747</ref>.   Amakuru ya Kemi Filani yanenze iyi filime, avuga ko ikubiyemo "gukina nabi, kuvuga inkuru ziteye isoni, gukomeza kubaho nabi, gutura ahantu hamwe n'ibibazo byinshi bibabaza<ref>https://ajph.aphapublications.org/doi/10.2105/AJPH.2020.306125</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/view/group/main/main/id/00035346.html</ref>."

